@startuml SuperAdmin_UC01-10_Gerer_Secretariats
title UC-01-10: Gerer Secretariats - SuperAdmin (Tous Scenarios)

actor SuperAdmin as SA
participant Dashboard
participant Systeme
participant DB
participant Logs

SA -> Dashboard: 1. Accede a Gestion Secretariats
activate Dashboard

Dashboard -> DB: 2. Recupere liste tous secretariats
activate DB

alt Erreur BD indisponible
  DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR: BD down
  deactivate DB
  Dashboard --> SA: ERREUR 500: Impossible charger secretariats
  deactivate Dashboard
else BD disponible
  DB --> Dashboard: Retourne liste secretariats avec stats
  deactivate DB

  Dashboard --> SA: 3. Affiche tableau secretariats (nom, TVA, nb users, statut)
  deactivate Dashboard

  SA -> Dashboard: 4. Clique sur secretariat pour details
  activate Dashboard

  Dashboard -> DB: 5. Recupere details secretariat complets
  activate DB

  alt Secretariat inexistant
    DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR 404: Non trouve
    deactivate DB
    Dashboard --> SA: ERREUR: Secretariat inexistant
    deactivate Dashboard
  else Secretariat existe
    DB --> Dashboard: Retourne infos (TVA, IBAN, adresse, users, clients, plan)
    deactivate DB

    Dashboard --> SA: 6. Affiche fiche detaillee secretariat
    deactivate Dashboard

    SA -> Dashboard: 7. Clique Modifier
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard --> SA: 8. Affiche formulaire (TVA, IBAN, adresse, contacts)
    deactivate Dashboard

    SA -> Dashboard: 9. Modifie champs et Sauvegarder
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> Systeme: 10. Valide format TVA et IBAN
    activate Systeme

    alt Format invalide
      Systeme --> Dashboard: ERREUR: TVA/IBAN format incorrect
      deactivate Systeme
      Dashboard --> SA: ERREUR: Format invalide
      deactivate Dashboard
    else Format valide
      deactivate Systeme

      Dashboard -> Systeme: 11. Detecte changements sensibles (TVA, IBAN modifies)
      activate Systeme
      Systeme --> Dashboard: Changements detectes
      deactivate Systeme

      Dashboard --> SA: 12. Affiche resume changements avec avertissement
      deactivate Dashboard

      SA -> Dashboard: 13. Confirme modifications
      activate Dashboard

      Dashboard -> DB: 14. Met a jour secretariat en transaction atomique
      activate DB

      alt Transaction echouee (conflit)
        DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Autre admin modifie simultanement
        deactivate DB
        Dashboard --> SA: ERREUR: Donnees modifiees, ressayez
        deactivate Dashboard
      else Transaction reussie
        DB -> DB: 15. UPDATE secretariat

        DB -> DB: 16. INSERT log modification (admin, changements, timestamp)

        DB --> Dashboard: Modifications confirmees
        deactivate DB

        Dashboard -> DB: 17. Enregistre log audit: Modification secretariat (admin, changements, timestamp)
        activate DB
        DB --> Dashboard: Audit log enregistre en BD
        deactivate DB

        Dashboard -> Logs: 18. Log event: Modification secretariat OK
        activate Logs
        Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue pour monitoring
        deactivate Logs

        Dashboard --> SA: 19. SUCCES! Modifications sauvegardees
        deactivate Dashboard

        note over SA, Logs
          **MODIFICATION OK:**
          - Secretariat mis a jour
          - Validations OK
          - DB: Audit logs persistes
          - Logs: Events loggues
          - Transaction atomique
        end note
      end
    end

    SA -> Dashboard: 19. Clique Voir historique
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> DB: 20. Recupere historique changements (30 derniers jours)
    activate DB
    DB --> Dashboard: Retourne logs modifications
    deactivate DB

    Dashboard --> SA: 21. Affiche historique complet
    deactivate Dashboard

    SA -> Dashboard: 22. Clique Suspendre secretariat
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard --> SA: 23. Affiche confirmation avec avertissement
    deactivate Dashboard

    SA -> Dashboard: 24. Confirme suspension
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> DB: 25. Marque secretariat SUSPENDU
    activate DB

    DB -> DB: 26. Log suspension (raison, admin, timestamp)

    DB --> Dashboard: Secretariat suspendu
    deactivate DB

    Dashboard -> DB: 27. Enregistre log audit: Suspension secretariat (admin, raison, timestamp)
    activate DB
    DB --> Dashboard: Audit log enregistre en BD
    deactivate DB

    Dashboard -> Logs: 28. Log event: Suspension secretariat OK
    activate Logs
    Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue pour monitoring
    deactivate Logs

    Dashboard --> SA: 29. SUCCES! Secretariat suspendu
    deactivate Dashboard

    note over SA, Logs
      **SUSPENSION OK:**
      - Secretariat marque SUSPENDU
      - Acces bloque
      - DB: Audit logs persistes
      - Logs: Events loggues
    end note
  end
end

@enduml
